*audacious-plugins-1.2.0 (18 Sep 2006)

  18 Sep 2006; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> +metadata.xml,
  +audacious-plugins-1.2.0.ebuild:
  Initial commit, ebuild by me.

